### Who I Am
I am Keith Avery, a developer and student in California. I develop for iOS and for the web, and am working towards a degree in Computer Science.

More information about me can be found on [my website](kpavery.com).

### Projects
[GOLDMine](https://github.com/kpavery/goldmine) - a browser extension to help UCSB students use their schedule how they like
